'''耶斯帕·居德'''，全名'''耶斯帕·居德·雅各布松'''（{{lang-da|'''Jesper Kyd Jakobson'''}}，{{bd|1972年|2月3日||}}），[[丹麦|丹麦]][[电子游戏|电子游戏]]及[[电影配乐|电影配乐]]作曲家。其作品结合了[[黑暗氛围|黑暗氛围]]、[[电子音乐|电子音乐]]与[[交响乐|交响乐]]的特征，曾获GameSpot特別成就獎<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2008/02/18/jesper-kyd-honored-at-elan-awards |title=Jesper Kyd Honored at ELAN Awards |date=2012-05-12 |website=IGN.com |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]] |accessdate=2022-03-14 |quote= }}</ref>等多个奖项。他还以早年在[[Amiga|Amiga]]Demoscene上的作品知名。他后来参与了《[[杀手系列|杀手系列]]》、《[[刺客信条|刺客信条]]系列》<ref name=Tamburro>{{cite web |url=http://www.craveonline.co.uk/site/873359-assassins-creed-composer-jesper-kyd-creative-process-favorite-soundtrack |title=Assassin's Creed Composer Jesper Kyd on the Creative Process and His Favorite Soundtrack |author=Paul Tamburro |date=2005-07-01 |access-date=2018-06-29 |work=[[Crave_Online|Crave Online]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170808114247/http://www.craveonline.co.uk/site/873359-assassins-creed-composer-jesper-kyd-creative-process-favorite-soundtrack |archive-date=2017-08-08}}</ref>以及《[[虚幻竞技场3|虚幻竞技场3]]》<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hexus.net/gaming/features/industry/5268-jesper-kyd-unreal-tournament-2007/ |title=Jesper Kyd: Unreal Tournament 2007 |author=Steven Williamson |date=2006-04-13 |work=[[Hexus|Hexus]] |publisher=[[The_Media_Team|The Media Team]] |access-date=2018-06-19}}</ref>的配乐工作。

